## Installation

# References
https://spark.apache.org/downloads.html

# Installation steps
<---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
wget http://www-eu.apache.org/dist/spark/spark-2.3.1/spark-2.3.1-bin-hadoop2.7.tgz
mkdir /opt/spark
tar xzf spark-2.3.1-bin-hadoop2.7.tgz -C /opt/spark --strip-components=1
cd /opt/spark

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------->


## Configurating spark standalone

# References
https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/spark-standalone.html

# Configuration steps for master
<---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ./sbin/start-master.sh --webui-port <port> -h <IP>
./sbin/start-master.sh --webui-port 9000 -h <IP>

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------->

# Configuration steps for slave
<---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ./sbin/start-slave.sh <master-spark-URL>

